name: Vessels 199: Protocol Death
description:
In order to operate as efficiently as possible, the AI known as Protocol Alpha can uses 4 distinct avatars depending on what skills will be needed to achieve their current objective. Each of these avatars is a distinct personality and yet still a part of the whole.

Protocol Death. Though they might sound like quite an intimidating and frightening figure, Protocol Death is ACTUALLY a VERY intimidating and frightening figure. An AI devoted to the mastery of dispensing death in every conceivable form. Few people see Protocol Death coming, and for those that do they are the last thing they ever see.

Animation and Sound by the fantastic sirgulliver.art
